Save time and money by automating your work. Record macros or use the easy script language to automate and control all your Windows applications, automate software processes and assign tasks to schedules, desktop shortcuts or hotkeys. Perform complex tasks with a single mouse click, or schedule your computer to perform tasks while you are away. With Macro Scheduler you can perform tasks and easily create macros.

The simple natural-English script language is designed for anyone to pick up, with features for controlling any Windows application and powerful technology such as Screen Image Recognition and Screen Scraping Text Capture.
